	title = {Development of a testbed to intelligent systems on software defined radio},
	doi = {10.1109/IMOC.2005.1579993},
	abstract = {The advances in wireless communication grew so much since the 90's, that a unique platform was required as a new alternative to this all portable devices. Therefore, this is not possible without using {DSPs} and {FPGAs} as a reconfigurable hardware. This tendency implicates in a new concept called software defined radio. In the University of Brasilia, there is a study group in {SDR} and its applications. This article will present the work done so far, as well as the difficulties that have to be surpassed in the process of developing of a software defined radio testbed.},
